@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pniffs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.16)) - 0.91)
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.74 + v1 + 0.49)) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.18) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.40)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = v2
    tmp = 0.79
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.00 * v0 + 0.91)) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.13 * tmp + 0.60)))
    data[tid] = v0
